Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.21,0:00:05.00,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Teman-teman yang bangkit kembali
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.08,0:00:07.88,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}bersatu kembali dengan Fushi.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.13,0:00:13.30,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Lalu…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.88,0:00:18.51,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kita bisa berkumpul di sini seperti ini\Nkarena hati kita terhubung!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.90,0:00:27.61,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aoki, Mizuha menghilang.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.69,0:00:29.61,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dia menghilang sejak dua hari lalu…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.84,0:02:14.30,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dia menghilang.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.01,0:02:20.89,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ketua Hanna!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.89,0:02:23.72,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Akhirnya kami menemukanmu.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.81,0:02:25.85,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ketua, kau baik-baik saja?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.85,0:02:30.40,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku baik-baik saja.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.48,0:02:33.11,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kami juga akan membantumu\Nmencari Kak Mizuha.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.19,0:02:36.65,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Wakil Kepala Sekolah dan yang lainnya\Npergi ke kota untuk mencari.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.74,0:02:40.53,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kalau begitu, mari berpencar\Ndan mencari di sekitar sini.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.16,0:02:44.87,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku ingat melihat Kak Mizuha\Ndi sini dua hari lalu.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.95,0:02:48.91,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dia pergi ke arah sini.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.96,0:02:52.75,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ke mana dia pergi?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.84,0:03:02.89,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aduh!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.60,0:03:11.65,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Keren! Luka sekeren luka Pak Kai.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.10,0:03:13.52,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Yuki, apa yang kau lakukan?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.61,0:03:15.61,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Fushi, sedang apa kau di sini?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.69,0:03:17.90,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku merasakan sensasi sakit.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.99,0:03:19.99,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Salah satunya berasal darimu.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.07,0:03:22.70,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau bahkan bisa merasakannya?\NLuar biasa!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.78,0:03:25.16,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kazumitsu dan Aiko mencemaskanmu.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.24,0:03:26.16,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ayo, kita pulang.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.24,0:03:29.37,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tunggu, Kak Mizuha menghilang.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.45,0:03:31.25,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku sedang mencarinya.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.33,0:03:32.25,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mizuha?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.46,0:03:37.55,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku ingat kakinya terluka.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.30,0:03:40.17,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kurasa aku tahu di mana rasa sakitnya.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.26,0:03:42.13,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Benarkah? Luar biasa.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.22,0:03:43.51,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku hanya perlu memastikan dia aman,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.59,0:03:45.39,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}lalu memulangkannya, bukan?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.89,0:03:47.10,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Akan kucoba.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.39,0:03:52.39,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mizuha!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.48,0:03:55.27,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dia pasti kesulitan.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.23,0:04:01.11,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kuharap dia tidak melakukan hal bodoh.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.83,0:04:16.58,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ketua Hanna!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.67,0:04:18.70,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Wakil Kepala Sekolah beri tahu kejadiannya.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.80,0:04:19.95,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau bisa flu jika begini.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.05,0:04:22.42,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Naiklah. Kita akan berkeliling mencarinya.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.51,0:04:23.88,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Baiklah.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.01,0:04:26.01,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau baik-baik saja?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.09,0:04:28.60,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau harus pulang.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.68,0:04:30.02,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku baik-baik saja.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.10,0:04:32.68,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku lebih mengkhawatirkan\Nkeselamatan Mizuha.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.27,0:04:36.90,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Siapa kau?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.86,0:04:45.11,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sakit.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.20,0:04:48.62,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku masih belum terbiasa\Nmemakai sepatu hak tinggi.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.70,0:04:50.45,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Siapa kau? Sedang apa kau di sini?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.54,0:04:52.08,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Maafkan aku. Aku Poco…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.16,0:04:54.37,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku semacam kakaknya Yuki.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.46,0:04:56.75,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bukan, sepupunya. Dari pihak ibunya.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.83,0:04:59.42,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sepupu Yuki… Kenapa kau di sini?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.50,0:05:02.38,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dia memintaku membantumu.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.46,0:05:04.05,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Semua orang mencemaskanmu.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.13,0:05:05.97,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ayo, kita pergi.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.05,0:05:09.01,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mizuha, apa itu temanmu?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.10,0:05:11.68,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Seharusnya beri tahu lebih awal.\NAku bisa siapkan teh.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.77,0:05:14.02,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kakek, tidak apa-apa.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.10,0:05:17.77,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}- Aku akan pulang.\N- Jadi, ini rumah kakekmu.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.19,0:05:20.07,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jangan memaksakan diri.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.44,0:05:21.73,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jika tidak mau tinggal di rumah,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.82,0:05:23.44,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}kau boleh datang kapan saja.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.94,0:05:24.99,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Terima kasih, Kakek.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.57,0:05:28.49,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kakak, ayo.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.46,0:05:38.50,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mizuha.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.55,0:05:43.96,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Senior, aku sangat mencemaskanmu.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.05,0:05:45.80,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau terluka?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.88,0:05:48.39,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Maaf, aku baik-baik saja.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.76,0:05:51.89,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Syukur kau baik-baik saja.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.52,0:05:54.35,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Maafkan aku.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.23,0:05:58.02,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mungkinkah kau Fushi…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.36,0:06:04.11,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mizuha, apa sebenarnya maumu?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.19,0:06:05.36,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau pergi ke mana?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.44,0:06:06.78,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku pergi ke rumah Kakek.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.24,0:06:08.95,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dia membawamu dengan paksa, bukan?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.03,0:06:10.91,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku takkan memaafkannya.\NIni penculikan.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.99,0:06:11.87,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku akan menelepon polisi.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.95,0:06:13.20,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tunggu! Ibu salah!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.29,0:06:14.83,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku pergi ke rumah Kakek sendiri.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.45,0:06:18.37,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau bahkan tak masuk sekolah\Nhanya demi menemui kakekmu?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.00,0:06:21.29,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa Ibu melakukan sesuatu\Nyang membuatmu kesal?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.71,0:06:24.25,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tidak. Ini salahku.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.34,0:06:27.93,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku sudah lama tidak bertemu Kakek,\Njadi, aku merasa agak kesepian.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.01,0:06:30.97,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dia mengatakan\Natau melakukan sesuatu padamu?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.05,0:06:34.47,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tidak, dia hanya menunjukkan sebuah buku.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.56,0:06:35.72,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Buku?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.14,0:06:40.60,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Entah apa kau menyadarinya,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.69,0:06:42.90,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}tapi kakekmu dan Ibu tidak akur.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.65,0:06:44.73,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku tahu.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.82,0:06:48.20,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kalau begitu, jangan lakukan apa pun\Nyang akan membuat Ibu sedih.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.40,0:06:50.61,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Maafkan aku.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.20,0:06:53.12,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Baguslah kau tahu.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.99,0:06:56.87,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Semuanya, terima kasih\Natas bantuan kalian hari ini.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.95,0:06:59.00,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku akan berterima kasih\Ndengan benar nanti.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.08,0:07:02.96,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku senang mengetahui Mizuha\Npada akhirnya punya teman-teman baik.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.54,0:07:04.63,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}"Pada akhirnya."
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.63,0:07:07.84,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku akan pindah.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.05,0:07:11.22,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Lihat, ini rumah baru kita.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.30,0:07:14.18,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku ingin mencocokkan tirai ini\Ndengan lantai.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.26,0:07:15.10,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bagaimana?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.06,0:07:16.93,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kurasa itu bagus.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.02,0:07:18.48,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mizuha, jangan bergerak.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.56,0:07:20.39,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mari kita berfoto untuk bulan ini.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.24,0:07:32.87,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jika kau pergi, Mizuha,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.24,0:07:34.70,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}aku akan menangis.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.78,0:07:35.83,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hanna.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.79,0:07:42.33,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jika ada yang ingin\Nkau katakan, katakanlah.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.42,0:07:45.67,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jangan menahan diri.\NAku bersedia menerima semuanya.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.50,0:07:47.71,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku ingin…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.34,0:07:51.01,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}tetap di sini.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.68,0:08:01.60,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau sudah dengar?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.69,0:08:02.90,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mizuha dari Kelas 1.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.98,0:08:04.94,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kudengar dia kabur dari rumah.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.56,0:08:07.73,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ya, aku sudah dengar. Dia sangat berani.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.82,0:08:10.99,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Biasanya yang pendiam\Nyang paling menakutkan saat marah.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.07,0:08:14.87,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku melihatnya bicara\Ndengan orang asing tempo hari.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.95,0:08:16.37,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sungguh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.29,0:08:20.54,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mizuha, ayo ke ruang klub.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.41,0:08:22.58,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Baiklah.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.17,0:08:30.26,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bulu itu… Aku yang membuatnya.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.34,0:08:31.38,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau rupanya.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.47,0:08:32.29,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Maafkan aku.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.38,0:08:34.67,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kulihat kau tinggalkan di ruang klub,\Njadi, kupakai untuk mengikat rambutku.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.76,0:08:37.72,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tidak apa-apa. Aku membuatnya untukmu.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.79,0:08:39.05,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sudah kuduga.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.14,0:08:41.05,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Omong-omong, bagaimana kakimu?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.14,0:08:42.80,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku bisa berlari sekarang.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.89,0:08:45.06,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jangan terlalu memaksakan diri.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.40,0:08:47.48,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau mulai lagi.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.56,0:08:50.61,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kita bukan Klub Otaku\Natau Klub Riset Hal Gaib.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.19,0:08:54.07,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kita Klub Sastra Kreatif.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.61,0:08:56.70,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bagaimana pindahanmu?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.78,0:08:57.99,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku belum yakin.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.08,0:08:59.16,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Begitu rupanya.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.24,0:09:01.62,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kenapa tak kau bicarakan lagi dengan ibumu?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.70,0:09:03.00,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Katakan kau tidak mau.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.54,0:09:06.04,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Selamat pagi, dua seniorku!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.12,0:09:08.54,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Yuki, kau mengejutkanku.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.63,0:09:09.88,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ini bukan pagi lagi.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.96,0:09:10.88,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau benar.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.96,0:09:12.42,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tapi begitulah cara kerja industri.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.71,0:09:15.93,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mizuha, aku yakin\Nsemua akan berjalan lancar.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.56,0:09:29.23,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mizuha, Ibu akan mencuci blus dan gaun ini.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.31,0:09:31.61,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Baik, Bu. Terima kasih.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.70,0:09:40.95,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}- Ibu, aku ingin bilang…\N- Mizuha, maafkan aku.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.03,0:09:45.66,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sebagai ibumu, seharusnya Ibu\Nmengerti alasanmu kabur.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.75,0:09:47.33,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Yang paling mengecewakanku
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.42,0:09:50.84,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}adalah hati Mizuha makin menjauh dari Ibu.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.92,0:09:53.51,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jadi, Ibu memutuskan untuk tidak pindah.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.59,0:09:57.13,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ibu, terima kasih.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.22,0:09:58.39,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku senang sekali.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.27,0:10:10.23,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ibu melihat ikat rambut buluku?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.31,0:10:12.36,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tidak. Kau sudah mencari dengan teliti?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.44,0:10:15.65,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tidak ada di keranjang cucian. Itu aneh.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.74,0:10:17.82,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku yakin meninggalkannya di wastafel.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.91,0:10:19.91,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa boleh buat jika kau menghilangkannya.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.20,0:10:21.66,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ulurkan tanganmu.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.79,0:10:24.91,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ini…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.00,0:10:28.50,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ini ikat rambut favorit Ibu saat SD.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.58,0:10:32.71,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ibu harap kelak bisa Ibu gunakan\Nuntuk mengikat rambut anak semanis Mizuha,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.79,0:10:36.38,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}jadi, Ibu merawatnya dengan baik.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.47,0:10:38.43,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa boleh benda sepenting ini untukku?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.51,0:10:40.93,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bagaimana jika hilang lagi?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.01,0:10:43.39,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tidak apa-apa. Berbaliklah.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.94,0:10:51.52,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Lihat, itu sangat cocok untukmu.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.44,0:10:55.44,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau putri Ibu yang berharga.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.28,0:11:00.95,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku sungguh minta maaf!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.24,0:11:03.95,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku kehilangan ikat rambut\Nyang kau berikan.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.03,0:11:05.41,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jangan khawatir.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.49,0:11:07.33,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Memakai ikat rambut yang sama itu bagus,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.41,0:11:10.67,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}tapi meski hilang,\Nikatan kita tidak akan putus.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.75,0:11:11.88,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hanna.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.96,0:11:14.17,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sebenarnya, aku senang itu hilang.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.25,0:11:18.88,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kehilangan itu membuatku sadar\Nbetapa ibumu memedulikanmu.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.34,0:11:21.43,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ikat rambut ini sangat cocok untukmu.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.51,0:11:22.59,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Benarkah?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.68,0:11:24.64,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau juga tidak perlu pindah lagi.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.56,0:11:27.68,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jika aku mengajakmu pergi sekarang,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.77,0:11:28.85,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}ibumu takkan marah, kan?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.93,0:11:30.31,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa maksudmu?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.39,0:11:33.31,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ayo ke mal stasiun akhir pekan ini.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.40,0:11:34.65,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku ingin beli cermin tangan.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.44,0:11:37.73,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku akan tanya Ibu nanti.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.45,0:11:42.66,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Manisnya! Ini juga bagus.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.74,0:11:49.71,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Baiklah, aku akan membeli yang ini.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.33,0:11:52.04,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Terima kasih banyak.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.54,0:11:55.29,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Itu cocok untukmu.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.88,0:11:58.88,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau dipuji!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.01,0:12:02.68,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Yang ini manis!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.76,0:12:03.59,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Yang mana?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.68,0:12:05.01,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kurasa aku mau beli ini.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.18,0:12:09.39,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Itu bagus. Benar-benar cocok untukmu.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.81,0:12:13.56,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mari beli jepit rambut kembar ini.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.65,0:12:14.61,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Baiklah.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.69,0:12:16.73,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ada toko krep baru di lantai tiga.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.82,0:12:17.82,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau pernah ke sana?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.90,0:12:18.90,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tidak.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.44,0:12:20.49,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ayo.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.41,0:12:35.46,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tentu saja, makan dua porsi\Nsangat mengenyangkan.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.54,0:12:37.50,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ibu mungkin akan memarahiku nanti.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.59,0:12:38.75,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau makan terlalu banyak.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.84,0:12:40.80,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku masih dalam masa pertumbuhan.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.63,0:12:44.72,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hidup terasa cukup tenang, bukan?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.77,0:12:52.81,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kenapa kau menangis?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.40,0:12:57.81,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mari pergi bersama lagi lain kali.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.19,0:13:02.11,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku pulang.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.19,0:13:03.20,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Selamat datang.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.28,0:13:05.32,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mizuha, kau bersenang-senang?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.70,0:13:07.99,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.28,0:13:10.79,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mizuha?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.67,0:13:17.84,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Banyak orang di sekitarku
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.92,0:13:20.25,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}berpikir aku sempurna
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.34,0:13:22.26,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}dan punya semua yang kubutuhkan.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.13,0:13:24.97,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku juga berpikir begitu.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.80,0:13:27.43,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa pun itu,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.51,0:13:29.85,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}aku belajar lebih cepat dari yang lain.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.51,0:13:32.31,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Akademik bukan masalah bagiku.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.31,0:13:36.69,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Banyak orang memujiku dalam olahraga juga.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.77,0:13:40.02,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kalau begitu, Mizuha akan berada di tengah.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.11,0:13:42.69,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kenapa selalu dia?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.19,0:13:44.86,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Gerakan ini mudah.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.95,0:13:46.74,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Semua pasti bisa melakukannya.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.58,0:13:52.33,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kenapa kau tidak bisa melakukan\Nhal semudah itu?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.66,0:13:54.66,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kukira aku sempurna.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.75,0:13:56.62,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tapi saat aku masuk SMP,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.71,0:13:59.29,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}aku sadar ada hal\Nyang tidak bisa kumiliki juga.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.38,0:14:01.92,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hebat! Mizuha,\Nkau membuat kaligrafi dengan baik.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.00,0:14:03.42,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Benar sekali!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.51,0:14:06.22,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Yang pertama adalah teman yang sempurna.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.30,0:14:08.22,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau mau berkencan denganku?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.30,0:14:09.14,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Maafkan aku.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.22,0:14:11.76,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku benci orang-orang yang di bawahku.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.85,0:14:15.64,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tidak ada gunanya\Nbersama orang yang tidak bisa kuhormati.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.31,0:14:18.65,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Yang kedua adalah ibu yang sempurna.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.73,0:14:22.11,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ibuku menyuruhku\Nbelajar banyak hal sejak aku kecil.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.57,0:14:24.61,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku bukan membencinya.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.69,0:14:26.90,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku bisa melakukan apa pun.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.99,0:14:29.24,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ibu, lihat piala ini.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.28,0:14:33.41,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mizuha, kaulah alasan Ibu hidup.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.49,0:14:36.62,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bagi Ibu, aku hanya piala.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.33,0:14:42.21,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ketiga adalah waktu yang hanya bisa\Ndigunakan untuk menyenangkan Ibu.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.67,0:14:45.55,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Waktu yang kekal, muda yang tak lekang.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.63,0:14:48.01,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sekeras apa pun aku berusaha,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.09,0:14:50.68,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}kerutan tetap akan muncul\Ndi sekitar mataku.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.76,0:14:52.22,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Itu jelek.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.30,0:14:54.56,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku sempurna karena masih muda.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.64,0:14:56.68,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Setelah tua, aku hanya\Nakan menjadi orang biasa.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.10,0:14:59.65,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku ingin mati.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.06,0:15:01.73,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tanpa kusadari,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.81,0:15:06.36,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}aku mulai bermimpi\Nmengakhiri hidupku sebelum aku dewasa.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.15,0:15:10.11,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku tahu kepribadian ini tidak baik.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.49,0:15:13.03,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tapi aku benar-benar\Ntidak bisa mengubahnya.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.12,0:15:18.08,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Andai saja seseorang\Nbisa menyadarkanku kelak.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.16,0:15:20.75,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hanna, kau juga harus waspada.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.83,0:15:23.25,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sebenarnya, dia suka mempermainkan pria.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.34,0:15:24.42,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tidak mungkin!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.50,0:15:27.01,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dia tidak seluang itu.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.34,0:15:31.39,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jangan khawatir.\NAda orang yang bersedia menangkapku.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.01,0:15:35.31,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Orang yang akan menerima\Nsosok yang dibenci sepertiku.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.64,0:15:39.77,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jika aku mati,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.14,0:15:41.40,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}kau akan menangis untukku?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.15,0:15:47.03,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kukira dia bisa menangkapku.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.11,0:15:49.07,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tapi dia tidak langsung menjawab.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.44,0:15:51.57,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Itu membuatku sedih.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.61,0:15:55.20,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jangan abaikan lukamu.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.50,0:16:04.42,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Saat dewasa, kita akan menghadapi\Nlebih banyak rintangan.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.50,0:16:08.38,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Pekerjaan, keluarga, hubungan, harga diri.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.09,0:16:13.09,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku mungkin akan mati\Nsekitar usia 17 tahun.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.09,0:16:16.89,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kita akan pindah bulan depan,\Njadi, bersiaplah.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.68,0:16:20.68,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ibu bilang kita akan pindah.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.40,0:16:27.90,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sudah kularang Ayah mengirim surat lagi.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.78,0:16:32.49,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Penyesalan.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.78,0:16:35.62,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku tidak bisa menjelaskannya,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.70,0:16:38.33,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}tapi sesuatu masih tersisa di hatiku.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.41,0:16:42.21,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sejujurnya, aku sungguh tidak tahu\Napa yang Ibu pikirkan.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.29,0:16:45.88,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa aku masih\Nbelum cukup sempurna untuk Ibu?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.96,0:16:48.63,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku sedikit memberontak,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.25,0:16:51.09,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}menganggapnya seperti permainan.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.93,0:17:01.64,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mizuha, kenapa kau di sini?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.35,0:17:04.02,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau sudah beri tahu ibumu?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.09,0:17:05.34,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.31,0:17:10.73,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Begitu, ya. Kalau begitu,\Nibumu pasti bersedia menerimanya.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.60,0:17:15.49,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Menyerahkan Pasukan Pelindung\Nkepada Mizuha.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.95,0:17:18.45,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa itu Pasukan Pelindung?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.53,0:17:20.61,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Selama beberapa generasi, keluarga kita
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.70,0:17:23.41,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}terlibat dalam praktik keagamaan.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.04,0:17:28.25,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Di rumah kumuh ini?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.75,0:17:31.80,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau pasti bertanya-tanya\Ndi mana umatnya, bukan?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.88,0:17:35.01,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Karena seseorang tidak mengizinkan\Nkita berkhotbah secara terbuka,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.09,0:17:38.30,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}para umat tidak terlibat\Ndalam kegiatan misi.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.68,0:17:42.72,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau akan menjadi generasi ke-18,\Npimpinan kelompok saat ini.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.10,0:17:47.90,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tapi ibumu menolak,\Njadi, dia memutuskan hubungan denganku.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.77,0:17:50.36,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Maafkan aku, Kakek.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.44,0:17:53.57,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sebenarnya, aku datang hari ini\Ntanpa memberi tahu Ibu.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.65,0:17:56.11,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dia mungkin sibuk mencariku sekarang.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.28,0:17:58.57,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sepertinya kau bergembira.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.66,0:18:00.83,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku ingin tahu lebih\Nyang Kakek katakan tadi.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.91,0:18:02.91,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa yang dilindungi Pasukan Pelindung ini?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.87,0:18:06.29,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Monster abadi.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.92,0:18:09.59,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Penelitian ini masih menyimpan\Nsemua catatan hingga saat ini.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.67,0:18:11.30,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau bisa melihatnya.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.72,0:18:20.89,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Leluhurku adalah\Nseorang wanita bernama Hayase.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.97,0:18:23.97,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Semuanya dimulai\Nsaat dia melindungi monster itu.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.39,0:18:26.69,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Monster itu mampu menghidupkan kembali\Norang-orang di sekitarnya
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.77,0:18:28.15,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}dan menjadikan mereka sekutunya.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.56,0:18:31.11,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Pada saat itu,\Ndia menyelamatkan ibu kota kuno, Renril
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.19,0:18:35.19,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}dari ancaman makhluk legendaris\Nyang dikenal sebagai Nokker.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.86,0:18:38.11,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Nama monster itu adalah Fushi.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.53,0:18:42.53,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Itu hanya legenda.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.08,0:18:48.33,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dengar, Semuanya!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.42,0:18:50.58,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku menemukan Bocah Buas!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.67,0:18:52.34,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tentu saja, dia keluarga.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.42,0:18:54.84,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kakek dan adikku sangat menyayangi Fushi.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.01,0:19:04.52,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Semua orang mencemaskanmu.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.10,0:19:09.90,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tak ada yang bisa masuk lewat\Nsatu-satunya jendela ventilasi di sini.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.73,0:19:14.69,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aksi pemberontakanku\Nmembawaku ke penemuan besar.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.36,0:19:16.69,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Potongan teka-tekiku yang hilang.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.78,0:19:18.65,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sesuatu yang benar-benar kubutuhkan.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.03,0:19:21.66,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Alih-alih meratapi kekuranganku,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.74,0:19:25.70,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}aku lebih memilih memiliki sesuatu\Nyang melampaui segalanya.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.79,0:19:28.71,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jadi, aku bisa mencapai kesempurnaan\Nuntuk kali pertama dalam hidupku.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.58,0:19:31.00,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.83,0:19:33.50,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}menginginkan…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.67,0:19:36.13,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}dia.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.38,0:19:41.93,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ini aneh.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.01,0:19:45.01,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku belum pernah merasakan\Nkebahagiaan seperti ini.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.10,0:19:47.27,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mungkinkah saat kita punya\Ntujuan lebih besar,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.35,0:19:52.10,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}semua emosi negatif\Nakan menjadi tidak penting?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.44,0:19:58.03,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ikat rambut Ibu sangat cocok untukmu.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.11,0:20:01.11,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ibu yang tidak sempurna juga lumayan.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.91,0:20:03.16,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kak Mizuha!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.24,0:20:05.33,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aksesori rambut itu cantik sekali!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.41,0:20:07.91,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Benarkah? Ini harta karun ibuku.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.00,0:20:09.41,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Manis sekali!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.08,0:20:11.21,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Syukurlah.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.67,0:20:14.71,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Teman yang tidak sempurna juga lumayan.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.59,0:20:19.51,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hari-hari yang singkat\Ndan kacau itu juga lumayan.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.42,0:20:22.72,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jika ada yang kurang,\Naku akan menciptakannya.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.80,0:20:24.80,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Akan kucoba hubungkan titik-titiknya.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.18,0:20:32.19,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sejauh mana kesempurnaan hidupku\Nbisa tercapai oleh tanganku sendiri?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.86,0:20:39.90,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sampai jumpa, Mizuha.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.38,0:20:56.71,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.04,0:20:58.88,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kapan aku pulang?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.30,0:21:02.38,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa aku tertidur di lorong?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.26,0:21:10.10,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ayah?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.18,0:21:12.60,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mizuha, Ayah menginap\Ndi rumah orang tua Ayah hari ini.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.68,0:21:14.06,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau makanlah lebih dahulu.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.14,0:21:15.23,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Baiklah.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.31,0:21:17.11,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bagaimana dengan kaki Bibi?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.19,0:21:19.40,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tidak apa-apa. Dia sedang tidur.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.48,0:21:21.07,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tolong beri tahu Ibu.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.65,0:21:22.78,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sampai jumpa.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.86,0:21:26.24,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ibu, Ayah bilang\Ntidak akan pulang hari ini.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.75,0:21:33.00,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ibu!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.04,0:21:36.63,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ibu!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.55,0:21:46.01,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ibu.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.11,0:22:08.91,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa yang terjadi?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.99,0:22:10.16,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ibu.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.12,0:22:13.83,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kenapa aku melarikan diri?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.91,0:22:16.12,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku tidak ingat apa pun.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.25,0:22:18.33,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ayah.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.00,0:22:20.46,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku harus menghubungi Ayah…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.54,0:22:21.92,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa itu?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.00,0:22:23.59,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Astaga, jangan lihat.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.97,0:22:26.18,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ayo kita kejar.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.26,0:22:27.09,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau merekam ini?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.18,0:22:29.51,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hentikan. Ayo.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.47,0:22:32.39,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa aku membunuh Ibu?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.89,0:22:35.68,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Seseorang, tolong aku.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.77,0:22:39.90,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kenapa tidak meminta bantuan\Nke teman kesayanganmu
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.69,0:22:43.40,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}sebelum keadaan menjadi begini?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.15,0:22:48.28,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa ada yang bisa kubantu?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.99,0:22:52.78,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jadilah…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.66,0:22:56.04,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}temanku.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:31.80,0:24:34.80,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kota yang begitu tenang,\Nsampai terasa membosankan.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:35.39,0:24:40.35,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Di sudut gelap,\Ngadis muda itu membunuh ibunya.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:41.69,0:24:44.23,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Di bawah pengawasan\Norang-orang di sekitar mereka,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:44.65,0:24:47.77,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Fushi dan Mizuha makin dekat.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:48.36,0:24:52.91,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Lalu, peristiwa aneh terjadi.
